      <title>随着制裁安装，伊朗充满石油的油轮在马来西亚建立</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/iran-oil-filled-tankers-build-up-off-malaysia-as-sanctions-mount</link>
      <description><![CDATA[近十个美国批准的油轮正在用伊朗原油闲逛马来西亚，其中一些人驻扎在石油转移枢纽超过一个月以上＆mdash;对中国敏感贸易的物流放缓的可能迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/iran-oil-filled-tankers-build-up-off-malaysia-as-sanctions-mount</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 11:15:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
